1
00:01:21,039 --> 00:01:21,600
You...

2
00:01:21,600 --> 00:01:22,600
Don't speak.

3
00:01:40,800 --> 00:01:42,560
Son.

4
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:49,160
My son.

5
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:57,539
Your Highness.

6
00:01:59,039 --> 00:02:00,440
My condolences.

7
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:03,580
We will definitely find the murderer

8
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:05,960
and seek justice for the Heir.

9
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:09,000
Easy for you to say.

10
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:10,759
The manor has been peaceful.

11
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:11,880
Why did such things happen

12
00:02:11,880 --> 00:02:14,400
right after the Prime Minister and his party arrived?

13
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:16,000
Your Young Mistress is strange, too.

14
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:17,260
She never sees anyone.

15
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,360
My Lord.

16
00:02:23,160 --> 00:02:25,200
Master! Bad news, Master!

17
00:02:25,440 --> 00:02:25,900
Master!

18
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:27,520
Master, bad news!

19
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:28,360
How dare you!

20
00:02:29,200 --> 00:02:30,800
What is with this attire?

21
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,120
Master, bad news!

22
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:32,960
It's terrible!

23
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:35,090
The Young Miss drugged me and escaped.

24
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:42,240
I have heard

25
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:49,960
that your daughter is quite skilled in the healing arts.

26
00:02:51,880 --> 00:02:52,740
Your Highness.

27
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:56,320
My daughter does know a little about medicine.

28
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:58,400
She has also always refused the marriage.

29
00:02:58,400 --> 00:03:00,800
But I never expected she would actually...

30
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:02,180
Your Highness.

31
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:04,760
I have failed in my duty.

32
00:03:05,760 --> 00:03:07,400
I failed to keep a proper watch on Jibai.

33
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:09,360
Please rest assured, Your Highness.

34
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:12,040
I will definitely capture her and bring her back.

35
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:14,200
I will make her atone with her life.

36
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,600
Guards!

37
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:24,640
Seal off the manor!

38
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:27,320
Search every corner.

39
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:29,720
I want to see

40
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:33,000
what kind of monsters

41
00:03:33,480 --> 00:03:36,720
dare to cause trouble in my Zhenbei Manor.

42
00:03:43,640 --> 00:03:45,440
Go find the coroner

43
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:49,620
and investigate this matter carefully.

44
00:03:49,760 --> 00:03:50,400
Yes.

45
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:51,560
You,

46
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:56,320
assign one more person to guard the scene.

47
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:06,520
Your Highness.

48
00:04:36,760 --> 00:04:41,040
Father, I'm sorry to make you sad.

49
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:43,440
But I must investigate that matter thoroughly.

50
00:04:43,440 --> 00:04:45,300
I can't tell you I'm safe just yet.

51
00:04:46,520 --> 00:04:48,200
Where did this news come from?

52
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:51,480
It's a woman from out of town.

53
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:58,280
She has been secretly inquiring about the Heir Apparent.

54
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:03,600
She claims that the Heir Apparent is not your biological son,

55
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:09,440
but the descendant of... that Lord.

56
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:13,720
Absurd. Block all news of this kind.

57
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:16,760
Whoever dares to spread it will be severely punished.

58
00:05:16,760 --> 00:05:19,440
Keep a close watch on the Heir Apparent's movements. Before he gets married,

59
00:05:19,440 --> 00:05:22,080
he is not allowed to take a single step out of Zhenbei Prince's Manor.

60
00:05:22,080 --> 00:05:23,320
You must handle this properly.

61
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:24,080
Yes.

62
00:05:24,080 --> 00:05:27,680
The survival of the entire Zhenbei Prince's Manor depends on it.

63
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:32,000
What kind of true identity

64
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:35,440
could affect the survival of the Zhenbei Prince's Manor?

65
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,560
Stop!

66
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:50,200
Don't hurt anyone.

67
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:58,320
Son.

68
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:01,730
This is your future Princess Consort.

69
00:06:02,080 --> 00:06:05,520
You two are truly a perfect match.

70
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:11,440
Father.

71
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:13,400
At my age, I should be training in the army

72
00:06:13,400 --> 00:06:14,530
to serve my country.

73
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:16,440
Why get married so early?

74
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:18,120
To make her a living widow?

75
00:06:18,520 --> 00:06:19,400
Nonsense!

76
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:22,960
Why is she dressed like that?

77
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:27,600
I advise you to stay out of this.

78
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,160
Leave now.

79
00:06:39,080 --> 00:06:40,640
He was probably just knocked out.

80
00:06:40,640 --> 00:06:41,880
He is in no danger.

81
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:55,800
Li Si was supposed to be on duty with you today.

82
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:59,680
Why is he not in the manor right now?

83
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:02,600
The Heir called him to help this morning.

84
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,930
He asked him to go alone.

85
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:06,440
He hasn't returned since.

86
00:07:07,520 --> 00:07:10,720
Your Highness, could he be planning to harm the Heir?

87
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:44,440
Sure enough, he isn't the Heir.

88
00:07:45,440 --> 00:07:48,440
His face was ruined on purpose.

89
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:53,800
How dare you!

90
00:07:53,840 --> 00:07:55,040
You trespassed in the Heir's room

91
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:56,240
and touched his remains.

92
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:58,240
The Prince will punish you for this.

93
00:08:01,840 --> 00:08:04,560
Then please take me to see the Prince.

94
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:12,280
Your Highness, Prime Minister.

95
00:08:12,280 --> 00:08:13,960
She sneaked into the Heir's room

96
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:15,800
and touched the things inside.

97
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:17,840
You rebellious daughter!

98
00:08:19,440 --> 00:08:22,760
So you really are involved in the Heir's death.

99
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:29,160
I have promised the Prince that you will pay with your life.

100
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:34,400
Then don't blame me for disregarding our father-daughter bond.

101
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:35,679
Guards!

102
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:38,280
Seize her.

103
00:08:38,640 --> 00:08:39,720
Your Highness,

104
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:41,640
do you recognize this?

105
00:08:48,560 --> 00:08:50,600
It's you.

106
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:55,560
You are the young doctor who saved me back then.

107
00:08:55,560 --> 00:08:56,240
You...

108
00:08:59,160 --> 00:09:01,820
You are actually Prime Minister Ji's daughter.

109
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:08,560
Young Doctor Ji.

110
00:09:09,080 --> 00:09:10,200
In the blink of an eye,

111
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:11,920
you've grown up.

112
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:15,120
Is your master well?

113
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:17,000
My master is well.

114
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:19,000
He just dislikes crowds more and more,

115
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:20,920
and hasn't come down the mountain.

116
00:09:20,920 --> 00:09:21,920
Your Highness.

117
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:24,160
Do you know my daughter?

118
00:09:26,920 --> 00:09:28,720
I do more than just know her.

119
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:32,220
Back then, when I led the army,

120
00:09:32,520 --> 00:09:33,920
I was seriously injured.

121
00:09:34,640 --> 00:09:38,280
If not for Doctor Lingyue and Young Doctor Ji,

122
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:41,960
I would have died on the battlefield.

123
00:09:43,040 --> 00:09:44,360
You silly child.

124
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:46,440
Since you know His Highness,

125
00:09:46,640 --> 00:09:48,840
why didn't you tell me?

126
00:09:49,920 --> 00:09:51,440
Bring a chair, quickly.

127
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:52,360
Your Highness,

128
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:54,480
I cannot accept such a great honor.

129
00:09:55,040 --> 00:09:56,040
Thank you, Your Highness.

130
00:09:56,040 --> 00:09:57,760
I won't sit.

131
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:00,280
Would you like to sit?

132
00:10:05,560 --> 00:10:07,640
Your Highness, please do not grieve so much.

133
00:10:07,640 --> 00:10:09,970
That skeleton does not belong to the Heir.

134
00:10:12,880 --> 00:10:13,960
Really?

135
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:19,640
The ossification centers of that skeleton's costal cartilage have increased,

136
00:10:19,640 --> 00:10:22,440
and the manubrium and body of the sternum have fused.

137
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:25,300
This indicates the deceased was at least in his 30s,

138
00:10:25,560 --> 00:10:28,440
while the Heir has only just come of age.

139
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,280
In that case,

140
00:10:32,280 --> 00:10:36,240
the victim was likely Li Si.

141
00:10:38,040 --> 00:10:41,120
Ruyan, send for the steward.

142
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:41,640
Yes,

143
00:10:41,640 --> 00:10:42,500
Your Highness.

144
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:47,240
Thank you, Doctor Ji.

145
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:49,240
In addition,

146
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:51,570
I have another clue to tell Your Highness.

147
00:10:58,440 --> 00:11:01,360
It turns out the dead man is not the Heir.

148
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:06,440
Is that so?

149
00:11:08,440 --> 00:11:09,960
Fortunately, your courage is remarkable.

150
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:11,680
You placed a tracking scent on him,

151
00:11:11,680 --> 00:11:13,940
which makes it easier for me to catch him.

152
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:15,040
However, it was inconvenient,

153
00:11:15,040 --> 00:11:16,800
so I only brought a small dose.

154
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:19,400
I can prepare more in a while.

155
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,920
Your Highness needs to send a few hunting dogs.

156
00:11:21,920 --> 00:11:23,380
Once they catch the scent,

157
00:11:23,400 --> 00:11:25,330
they will be able to track him down.

158
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:27,460
Easier said than done.

159
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:30,800
If the scent can travel for thousands of miles,

160
00:11:30,920 --> 00:11:32,640
surely he will notice it too.

161
00:11:33,560 --> 00:11:35,090
If he discards his clothes,

162
00:11:36,040 --> 00:11:37,200
how will we find him?

163
00:11:38,520 --> 00:11:39,600
The scent is very faint.

164
00:11:39,600 --> 00:11:41,400
Only hunting dogs can detect it.

165
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:42,800
I trust her.

166
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:47,170
Thank you for your trouble, Physician Ji.

167
00:11:50,840 --> 00:11:53,000
Your Highness, the steward is here.

168
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:53,860
Your Highness.

169
00:11:55,480 --> 00:11:59,640
Physician Ji, please follow Ruyan to the pharmacy to prepare the medicine.

170
00:11:59,640 --> 00:12:01,760
I also happen to need the steward

171
00:12:01,760 --> 00:12:04,240
to arrange the funeral for the deceased.

172
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:08,840
Before I go, I have a request.

173
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:11,640
Why use the word "beg" between us?

174
00:12:12,520 --> 00:12:13,400
Speak freely.

175
00:12:15,600 --> 00:12:18,400
I studied medicine with my master from a young age.

176
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:20,600
At first, I was reluctant.

177
00:12:21,160 --> 00:12:23,520
But then a tragedy occurred,

178
00:12:23,840 --> 00:12:25,770
and I finally realized my calling.

179
00:12:26,800 --> 00:12:28,920
I never want anyone to suffer as I did,

180
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:33,200
watching helplessly as their dearest one dies before their eyes,

181
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:35,400
unable to do anything to help.

182
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:41,120
So I vowed to practice medicine and save lives,

183
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:42,980
making saving lives my priority.

184
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:43,640
I must not be negligent,

185
00:12:43,640 --> 00:12:44,900
and I must not retreat.

186
00:12:48,680 --> 00:12:50,240
I understand.

187
00:12:51,040 --> 00:12:53,320
You mean to break the engagement

188
00:12:53,840 --> 00:12:55,680
and resign?

189
00:12:58,320 --> 00:12:59,160
Nonsense.

190
00:13:00,160 --> 00:13:01,760
Only the lowly commoners

191
00:13:01,760 --> 00:13:05,400
would allow their women to show their faces in public.

192
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:07,920
You are the legitimate daughter of the Prime Minister's Manor,

193
00:13:07,920 --> 00:13:09,840
yet you wander around outside all day.

194
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:11,720
Have you no shame?

195
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:14,000
If I can save more lives,

196
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:15,720
so what if I am despised?

197
00:13:16,840 --> 00:13:17,900
Prime Minister Ji,

198
00:13:18,880 --> 00:13:21,280
you are not as insightful as your daughter.

199
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:24,840
If she and her master hadn't shown themselves in public back then,

200
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:27,370
I would have died on the battlefield long ago.

201
00:13:27,920 --> 00:13:30,240
How could I be meeting you here today?

202
00:13:30,680 --> 00:13:32,040
What Your Highness says

203
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:33,640
makes sense.

204
00:13:35,520 --> 00:13:39,160
If you really care about your child, you should support her

205
00:13:39,160 --> 00:13:41,760
and let her do what she thinks is right.

206
00:13:42,400 --> 00:13:44,840
After all, life is priceless.

207
00:13:45,880 --> 00:13:47,740
Healers have benevolent hearts,

208
00:13:48,080 --> 00:13:49,200
don't they?

209
00:13:52,560 --> 00:13:54,120
You are absolutely right, Your Highness.

210
00:13:54,120 --> 00:13:55,920
I am also deeply honored

211
00:13:55,920 --> 00:13:58,000
to do my humble part for the people.

212
00:13:58,240 --> 00:13:59,360
As for my request,

213
00:13:59,880 --> 00:14:01,840
I hope Your Highness can grant it.

214
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:03,360
Ji Bai.

215
00:14:03,920 --> 00:14:04,960
Physician Ji.

216
00:14:05,560 --> 00:14:07,800
If you are truly determined,

217
00:14:07,800 --> 00:14:09,330
I certainly won't stop you.

218
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:12,160
However,

219
00:14:13,240 --> 00:14:16,240
you are venturing out into the world alone.

220
00:14:16,240 --> 00:14:18,040
It's actually quite dangerous.

221
00:14:18,800 --> 00:14:20,660
My son is skilled in martial arts.

222
00:14:20,760 --> 00:14:22,000
Once I find him,

223
00:14:22,200 --> 00:14:23,200
you two can travel together.

224
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:24,600
Wouldn't that be better?

225
00:14:30,120 --> 00:14:32,720
Look, Jiujiu. This is a Buddha's Hand flower.

226
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:35,240
It's a very rare herb.

227
00:14:35,440 --> 00:14:36,760
You're amazing.

228
00:14:36,800 --> 00:14:39,440
You know all the plants on the mountain.

229
00:14:39,960 --> 00:14:43,320
Of course. I'm going to be like my master

230
00:14:43,320 --> 00:14:44,960
and become a miracle doctor.

231
00:14:45,520 --> 00:14:47,000
Then I'll become a hero.

232
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:49,160
You treat patients, and I'll protect you.

233
00:14:49,160 --> 00:14:51,240
We'll roam the world together

234
00:14:51,240 --> 00:14:53,360
and help those in need.

235
00:14:53,560 --> 00:14:56,120
Okay. When I can go down the mountain by myself,

236
00:14:56,120 --> 00:14:58,320
I'll come back to Sitai Town to find you.

237
00:14:58,320 --> 00:14:59,240
Let's pinky swear.

238
00:14:59,240 --> 00:15:00,360
No lying.

239
00:15:04,120 --> 00:15:05,000
No.

240
00:15:07,120 --> 00:15:08,400
I made a pact long ago

241
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:11,240
to travel the world together

242
00:15:11,480 --> 00:15:13,320
and practice medicine to save lives.

243
00:15:13,320 --> 00:15:15,320
I do not need your assistance, Heir.

244
00:15:47,800 --> 00:15:48,600
Liao, Chen, Luo, Deng.

245
00:15:48,600 --> 00:15:48,800
Xiao, Xiao, Xue, Que, Yi, Yi, Nan.

246
00:15:48,800 --> 00:15:49,760
Xiao, Xiao, Xue, Yi, Yi, Nan.

247
00:15:48,800 --> 00:15:49,760
Wu, Zhang, Li, Zheng, Chen, Luo, Deng.

248
00:15:49,760 --> 00:15:51,320
Xiao, Xiao, Xue, Yi.

249
00:16:17,200 --> 00:16:18,320
Ma, Miao, Lu, Ran.

250
00:16:18,400 --> 00:16:19,400
Ma, Miao, Lu, Ran.

251
00:16:22,840 --> 00:16:24,440
Lv, Sun, Zhang, Meng,

252
00:16:22,840 --> 00:16:24,440
Xiulong.

253
00:16:24,440 --> 00:16:25,000
Lv, Sun, Zhang.
